[[cdo:9 nguŏk 8 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[zh-min-nan:9 goe̍h 8 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[zh-yue:九月初八]] {{Lunisolar September}} '''September 8''' is the 8th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Tenshū (Wu Zhou)|ja|天授 (武周)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|690|ja|690|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Wu Zetian|ja|武則天|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} がEmperor・{{ill|Ruizong (Tang)|ja|睿宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} を廃し、Emperorに即位して国号を “{{ill|Zhou|ja|周|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ” とする * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1859|ja|1859|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Sonzōha|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の {{ill|Obama-han|ja|小浜藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 士・{{ill|Umeda Unhama|ja|梅田雲浜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} を京都で捕縛。{{ill|Ansei no Daigoku|ja|安政の大獄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が始まる * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year /{{ill|Meiji Gen|ja|明治元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Meiji Tennō|ja|明治天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が {{ill|Isshō Ichigen no Shō|ja|一世一元の詔|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} を発布し、{{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に {{ill|Change of era|ja|改元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1870|ja|1870|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 2|ja|10月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – 陸軍観兵式でイギリス人軍楽隊教師・{{ill|John William Fenton|ja|フェントン|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 作曲の『{{ill|Kimigayo|ja|君が代|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 』が初演奏 * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – 「海軍条例」制定。{{ill|Ministry of War (Meiji)|ja|兵部省|1=Ministry of War (pre-modern Japan)|lt=Ministry of War|qq= (pre-modern Japan)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に海軍部を設置
== Births == * {{ill|Hōkō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1727|ja|1727|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ii Naoshige|ja|井伊直禔|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、第10代{{ill|Hikone Domain|ja|彦根藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 主（+ {{ill|1754|ja|1754|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1864|ja|1864|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ikeda Kikunao|ja|池田菊苗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Chemist|ja|化学者|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （+ {{ill|1936|ja|1936|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} )
== Deaths == * {{ill|Itoku Tennō|ja|懿徳天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 35th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|紀元前477|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 6|ja|10月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Itoku Tennō|ja|懿徳天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、4代{{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1705|ja|1705|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 25|ja|10月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Yorishige|ja|徳川頼職|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、4代{{ill|Kishū Domain|ja|紀州藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 主・{{ill|Tokugawa Yoshimune|ja|Tokugawa Yoshimune|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の兄（* {{ill|1680|ja|1680|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) * {{ill|Annin|ja|安永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1775|ja|1775|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 2|ja|10月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kaga no Chiyome|ja|加賀の千代女|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （{{ill|Chiyone|ja|千代尼|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）、{{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （* {{ill|1703|ja|1703|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} )
