* {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year /{{ill|Meiji Gen|ja|明治元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Meiji Tennō|ja|明治天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  が {{ill|Isshō Ichigen no Shō|ja|一世一元の詔|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  を発布し、{{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  に {{ill|Change of era|ja|改元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 
