{{Not to be confused with|September 8 (Lunisolar)}}<!--hatnote--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:17, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月初八|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 8일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 8''' is the 8th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Butsumetsu|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Tenshū (Wu Zhou)|ja|天授 (武周)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshū (Wu Zhou)|qq=}} 1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|690|ja|690|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/690|qq=}} [[:en:October 16|October 16]] ） – [[:en:Wu Zetian|Wu Zetian]] がEmperor・[[:en:Yejong|Ruizong (Tang)]] を廃し、Emperorに即位して国号を “[[:en:Zhou dynasty|Zhou]] ” とする * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 6th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1859|ja|1859|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1859|qq=}} [[:en:October 3|October 3]] ） – {{ill|Sonzōha|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sonzōha|qq=}} の [[:en:Obama Domain|Obama-han]] 士・{{ill|Umeda Unhama|ja|梅田雲浜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Umeda Unhama|qq=}} を京都で捕縛。[[:en:Ansei Purge|Ansei no Daigoku]] が始まる * [[:en:Keiō|Keiō]] 4th year /{{ill|Meiji Gen|ja|明治元|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji Gen|qq=}} （[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1868|qq=}} [[:en:October 23|October 23]] ） – [[:en:Emperor Meiji|Meiji Tennō]] が {{ill|Isshō Ichigen no Shō|ja|一世一元の詔|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Isshō Ichigen no Shō|qq=}} を発布し、[[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] に {{ill|Change of era|ja|改元|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Change of era|qq=}} * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1870|ja|1870|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1870|qq=}} [[:en:October 2|October 2]] ） – 陸軍観兵式でイギリス人軍楽隊教師・[[:en:Fenton|John William Fenton]] 作曲の『[[:en:Kimigayo|Kimigayo]] 』が初演奏 * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 4th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871|qq=}} [[:en:October 21|October 21]] ） – 「海軍条例」制定。[[:en:Ministry of War (pre-modern Japan)|Ministry of War]] に海軍部を設置
== Births == * [[:en:Kyōhō|Hōkō]] 12nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1727|ja|1727|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1727|qq=}} [[:en:October 22|October 22]] ） – {{ill|Ii Naoshige|ja|井伊直禔|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ii Naoshige|qq=}} 、第10代[[:en:Hikone Domain|Hikone Domain]] 主（+ {{ill|1754|ja|1754|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1754|qq=}} ) * [[:en:Genji era|Genji]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1864|ja|1864|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1864|qq=}} [[:en:October 8|October 8]] ） – [[:en:Kikunae Ikeda|Ikeda Kikunao]] 、[[:en:Chemist|Chemist]] （+ {{ill|1936|ja|1936|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1936|qq=}} )
== Deaths == * [[:en:Emperor Itoku|Itoku Tennō]] 35th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|紀元前477|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[:en:October 6|October 6]] ） – [[:en:Emperor Itoku|Itoku Tennō]] 、4代[[:en:Emperor of Japan|Emperor]] * [[:en:Hōei|Hōei]] 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1705|ja|1705|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1705|qq=}} [[:en:October 25|October 25]] ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Yorishige|ja|徳川頼職|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Yorishige|qq=}} 、4代[[:en:Kishū Domain|Kishū Domain]] 主・{{ill|Tokugawa Yoshimune|ja|Tokugawa Yoshimune|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Yoshimune|qq=}} の兄（* {{ill|1680|ja|1680|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1680|qq=}} ) * {{ill|Annin|ja|安永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Annin|qq=}} 4th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1775|ja|1775|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1775|qq=}} [[:en:October 2|October 2]] ） – {{ill|Kaga no Chiyome|ja|加賀の千代女|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaga no Chiyome|qq=}} （{{ill|Chiyone|ja|千代尼|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chiyone|qq=}} ）、{{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/haiku poet|qq=}} （* {{ill|1703|ja|1703|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1703|qq=}} )
