== Events == * {{ill|Tenshū (Wu Zhou)|ja|天授 (武周)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshū (Wu Zhou)|qq=}} 1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|690|ja|690|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/690|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} [[:en:October 16|October 16]] ） – [[:en:Wu Zetian|Wu Zetian]] がEmperor・[[:en:Yejong|Ruizong (Tang)]] を廃し、Emperorに即位して国号を “[[:en:Zhou dynasty|Zhou]] ” とする * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 6th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1859|1859]] [[:en:October 3|October 3]] ） – {{ill|Sonzōha|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sonzōha|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} の [[:en:Obama Domain|Obama-han]] 士・{{ill|Umeda Unhama|ja|梅田雲浜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Umeda Unhama|qq=}} を京都で捕縛。[[:en:Ansei Purge|Ansei no Daigoku]] が始まる * [[:en:Keiō|Keiō]] 4th year /{{ill|Meiji Gen|ja|明治元|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji Gen|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} （[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1868|1868]] [[:en:October 23|October 23]] ） – [[:en:Emperor Meiji|Meiji Tennō]] が {{ill|Isshō Ichigen no Shō|ja|一世一元の詔|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Isshō Ichigen no Shō|qq=}} を発布し、[[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] に {{ill|Change of era|ja|改元|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Change of era|qq=}} * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1870|ja|1870|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1870|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:October 2|October 2]] ） – 陸軍観兵式でイギリス人軍楽隊教師・[[:en:Fenton|John William Fenton]] 作曲の『[[:en:Kimigayo|Kimigayo]] 』が初演奏 * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 4th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:October 21|October 21]] ） – 「海軍条例」制定。[[:en:Ministry of War (pre-modern Japan)|Ministry of War]] に海軍部を設置
== Births == * [[:en:Kyōhō|Hōkō]] 12nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1727|1727]] [[:en:October 22|October 22]] ） – {{ill|Ii Naoshige|ja|井伊直禔|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ii Naoshige|qq=}} 、第10代[[:en:Hikone Domain|Hikone Domain]] 主（+ [[:en:1754|1754]] ) * [[:en:Genji era|Genji]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1864|1864]] [[:en:October 8|October 8]] ） – [[:en:Kikunae Ikeda|Ikeda Kikunao]] 、[[:en:Chemist|Chemist]] （+ {{ill|1936|ja|1936|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1936|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} )
== Deaths == * [[:en:Emperor Itoku|Itoku Tennō]] 35th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:October 6|October 6]] ） – [[:en:Emperor Itoku|Itoku Tennō]] 、4代[[:en:Emperor of Japan|Emperor]] * [[:en:Hōei|Hōei]] 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1705|1705]] [[:en:October 25|October 25]] ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Yorishige|ja|徳川頼職|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Yorishige|qq=}} 、4代[[:en:Kishū Domain|Kishū Domain]] 主・{{ill|Tokugawa Yoshimune|ja|Tokugawa Yoshimune|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Yoshimune|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} の兄（* [[:en:1680|1680]] ) * {{ill|Annin|ja|安永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Annin|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 安永 (元号)}} 4th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1775|1775]] [[:en:October 2|October 2]] ） – {{ill|Kaga no Chiyome|ja|加賀の千代女|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaga no Chiyome|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 加賀千代女}} （{{ill|Chiyone|ja|千代尼|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chiyone|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 加賀千代女}} ）、{{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/haiku poet|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} （* [[:en:1703|1703]] )
